      "writtenOn": "2017-07-29T01:53:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t even want to estimate the complexity of this code.\nfor each extension it: (1) scans the whole string for it, and (2) appends it to another string, with possible reallocation and memcpy. How often is this called and what\u0027s the usual time spent?",
