      "lineNbr": 219,
      "author": {
        "id": 1082465
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-07-29T02:43:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It\u0027s just size of whitelist * size of extension string. I don\u0027t expect it to be called in any performance critical code. It\u0027s a few times per context creation.\n\nThe usual time spent is ~3-15 us. I decided to give up performance here for a simpler looking implementation.",
      "parentUuid": "a2dcaf1b_22defe3c",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 182,
        "startChar": 0,
